>>
>> The customer breakdown is now clear. Pallavaa is the only customer 
>> running 3-level approval. Poongodhai Spinning uses 1 level. SKS uses 
>> 1 level via EDP. Most others have PO_Approval=N. Sasi, document this 
>> in FSD Section 11 as the customer variation for PO_Approval.
>>
