>> exist but its name or URL has not been provided. Saravanan, please 
>> give the URL path or module name of the web approval screen currently 
>> used for PO approvals. This goes into FSD Section 10 as a Related 
>> Screen. It is the one item standing between this question and full 
>> closure.
>>
>>
